data.description:
Charming home in Lindale ISD recently remodeled in 2022 with fresh paint and new floors. When you walk in you will love the open concept/split master floor plan. The living room opens up to your kitchen and dining area, with the laundry room just adjacent. The fenced yard works nicely as a great play area for the kids or pets. Come see all this home has to offer, and call for your private showing today!

Renter responsible for all utilities and renters insurance is required. Pets allowed maximum 2, no restrictions. No smoking.
